OL,3,CAirline Jet2 announces two new Jersey
OL,4,Croutes
OL,6,FThe airline Jet2 has announced it will
OL,7,Fmore than double its capacity to and
OL,8,Ffrom Jersey, with expanded operations
OL,9,Fincluding two new routes next summer.
OL,11,FBirmingham flights will run on
OL,12,FTuesdays, Thursdays and Sundays from 2
OL,13,FMay to 10 October 2027.
OL,15,FA twice-weekly Bristol service will
OL,16,Falso begin on 14 May until 11 October
OL,17,Fnext year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
