OL,3,CAirline Jet2 announces two new Jersey
OL,4,Croutes
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Jet2 will offer extra seats
OL,7,Fon its existing Manchester route from
OL,8,F2 May to 31 October - with flights
OL,9,Fthree times a week between 2 May and
OL,10,F31 October 2027.
OL,12,FThe airline will also continue to
OL,13,Foperate its services to East Midlands,
OL,14,FLeeds Bradford and Newcastle
OL,15,FInternational airports.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
