OL,3,CAirline Jet2 announces two new Jersey
OL,4,Croutes
OL,6,FJet2's Chief Executive, Steve Heapy,
OL,7,Fsays: "We are delighted to be
OL,8,Fsignificantly expanding our Jersey
OL,9,Fprogramme for summer 2027, with a
OL,10,Fgreat choice of flights now departing
OL,11,Ffrom six UK airports as a result."
OL,13,FPorts of Jersey Chief Executive, Matt
OL,14,FThomas, adds: "The growth that Jet2
OL,15,Fhas announced for 2027 demonstrates
OL,16,Fthe growing confidence airlines have
OL,17,Fin Jersey.
OL,19,F"Increased capacity and a longer
OL,20,Fseason deliver greater choice and
OL,21,Fimproved connectivity."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
